QuestData.Title: Transdimensional Warfare: Chapter II
QuestData.Description: <The Banshee Queen's words float in your head.>$B$BYou are now ready to use the portal. Be warned, $n, once you step through you will appear in another dimension at Ambermill. There will be a hundred, perhaps a thousand, magi waiting to kill you.$B$BYou must persevere and kill all in your path.
QuestData.PortraitTurnInText: Their corpses will feed the Forsaken war machine!
QuestData.RewardText: <The Banshee Queen's voice invades your thoughts.>$B$BExcellent work, $n. Now to eject them into our waiting hands!
